name: FTPHub
body:
### FTPHub
FTPHub is my Java project for creating a simple to use FTP client with a nice user friendly GUI.

### Usage and Contributions
I would love to see some contributions if you want to improve on FTPHub, it has a long way to go but it is working right now :)

### Authors and Contributors
@bittiez is the Author of FTPHub, and FTPHub currently has no contributors.

### Support or Contact
You can send me a message through GitHub(Click the send message button in my profile @bittiez )
